interests.name: Venicci Circle
interests.description: The center of Venicci, with shopping and food
interests.review: Beautiful public area with a historic fountain. The tiney cafes are perfect for getting coffe in the morning and the shops that surround this gorgeous walkable area do not disappoint

interests.description: Hike to the top of the world!

interests.name: Gorilla Safari
interests.description: Jeep tour through conservation area - 6 hrs long
interests.review: If you are nervous about booking such an expensive trip, please be advised that you will have absolutely no issues with Gorilla Tours. If you can afford it time and money wise, book the extra gorilla day. You will want to see 2 different families as they are all different in behaviour and appearances!

interests.name: Marrakech Market
interests.description: A market for persian rugs, wooden bowls, spices, and
interests.review: This restaurant/ bar is a true find. Located just meters off Djema el Fna square it has an ambience and elegance not previously found on the square. Having just opened in December 2011 the service is superb and vibrant.

interests.name: Tre Cime Di Lavaredo
interests.description: National Park, UNESCO World Heritage Site
interests.review: For the people who loves mountain and trakking this is the first place in the world. I suggest to sleep the night before and have relax in the confortable hotels. In the early morning to start the walking all around the "3 ZINNEN" and have lunch in the typical mountain resaurant that are not very expensive.

interests.name: Hiking the Alps
interests.description: The best hiking and skiing in the world, hands down.
interests.review: The best hiking and skiing in the world, hands down. We hiked over 400 miles in 3 weeks while visiting here. You can hear the cowbells for miles.
